/svg></div><div class="leaflet-marker-pane"></div><div class="leaflet-popup-pane"></div></div></div><div class="leaflet-control-container"><div class="leaflet-top leaflet-left"><div class="leaflet-control-zoom leaflet-bar leaflet-control"><a class="leaflet-control-zoom-in" href="#" title="Zoom in">+</a><a class="leaflet-control-zoom-out" href="#" title="Zoom out">-</a></div></div><div class="leaflet-top leaflet-right"><div class="leaflet-control-grid map-tooltip leaflet-control" style="display: none;"><a class="close" href="#" title="close">close</a><div class="map-tooltip-content"></div></div></div><div class="leaflet-bottom leaflet-left"><div class="mapbox-logo leaflet-control"></div></div><div class="leaflet-bottom leaflet-right"><div class="map-legends wax-legends leaflet-control" style="display: none;"></div><div class="leaflet-control-attribution leaflet-control"><a href="https://www.mapbox.com/about/maps/" target="_blank">© Mapbox</a> <a href="https://openstreetmap.org/about/" target="_blank">© OpenStreetMap</a> <a class="mapbox-improve-map" href="https://www.mapbox.com/map-feedback/#mapbox.streets/-117.508/34.017/13" target="_blank">Improve this map</a></div></div></div></div><div id="result" class="tab-pane"></div><div id="export" class="tab-pane"><div class="exportHeader"><span>Export Options:</span></div><div id="exportChoice"><input id="exportCsv" type="radio" name="exportType" value="csv" checked="" class="exportType"><label for="exportCsv">CSV (Spreadsheet)</label><input id="exportGpx" type="radio" name="exportType" value="gpx" class="exportType"><label for="exportGpx">GPX (Tom Tom, Garmin)</label></div><div><div id="gpxOptions" style="display: none;"><form action="/export" method="post" style="display:inline"><input type="hidden" name="ext" value="gpx"><input id="exportContentGpx" type="hidden" name="content"><input id="downloadGpx" type="submit" value="Download GPX" class="btn btn-warning"></form></div><div id="csvOptions"><div><span class="exportOpt